Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.51,0:00:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Astro Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the sky, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.72,0:00:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the jet limit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A heart-warming la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a million-horsepower engine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.59,0:00:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.26,0:00:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be off your guard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A righteous la-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:00:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The child of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.26,0:01:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a seven-force power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mighty Atom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This sound is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.62,0:01:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear it outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's amplify my ear ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.11,0:02:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a footstep. Someone's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.96,0:02:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.29,0:02:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-A discus, it's coming to get water. -A discus and water?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be a disaster. Let everyone know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute. I'm Atom. Who in the world are...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Horett. I'm from Alsore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Alsore?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Be aware of the discus with the cross mark on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be some reason. Let's go inside the cabin first.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's dangerous. Run away! -Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did everyone go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Girl from Alsore
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Who is it? So early in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Ochanomizu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's Atom. Are you going to the ski resort?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about skiing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.21,0:03:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl I met last night told me she's from Alsore. What's Alsore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,-What? Alsore? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's... Ah! It was the name of a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of a planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.94,0:04:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know the details. Let me look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know either?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not an expert on planets. So where is that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Atom! Hello! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, Atom. He just left after asking his questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.31,0:04:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Alsore is the name of a planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.64,0:04:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.37,0:04:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-Come here, there's a problem. -What problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, I told you to go down the stairs one by one. How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.93,0:04:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,With the appearance of mysterious objects, paranormal activities are taking places everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.61,0:05:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The government recognized the seriousness of this and held a Cabinet meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They tried to explain this and prepare for any emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Discus, discus is coming to get water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Aliens are invading.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett. That's right. I have to go see Horett!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, we are going to go ski, so come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sucking up snow on the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the cross discus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful of that cross-marked discus. Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett might be caught in that one. Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.86,0:07:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You, to where did you take Horett?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys are robots, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.23,0:07:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to go easy on robots!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.54,0:07:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett, where are you? Horett!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett, you were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, but I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth people will never forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As you said, discuses are taking water away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,However, we can't stop robots and discuses that are already working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans started their attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Horett.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.70,0:07:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean robots and discuses moved on their own?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The 12th planet of Alsore always lacked water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We came to the Earth to ask for water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is a theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My mission was to meet the president of the Earth and ask to share water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,However, when we got close to the Earth, robots turned odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't listen to my commands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything got bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I got out and arrived at the Earth sooner than them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To let you guys know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But now it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay put here. Don't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll discuss this with Doctor Ochanomizu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett is not a bad one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You should let the Defense Department know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-It's too late, Atom. -Huh? Too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The hunt has begun over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The hunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.75,0:09:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There was an emergency command that they can kill anyone that's not from the Earth immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.53,0:09:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So Atom, this is the observation picture of Alsore planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What a temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.44,0:09:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I still worried about this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The light of this Alsore planet is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It has gotten ten times brighter in a month. This is maybe...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.54,0:10:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? I told you to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'd like to meet the president and apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not now. They started searching through mountains to catch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the police dog is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Reconnaissance plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:10:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The dog is near.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, doggy! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Dogs must have found it. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where? Where did the dogs go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, there's no one today. I can ski all I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-Something's wrong. -All humans must have ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,TV said a mysterious object is coming over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a problem. We should evacuate too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.57,0:12:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran! Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back...? Not that simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Uran.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to. I can finally ski since it's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.66,0:12:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's the one TV talked about!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran, Honey, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-Atom. -Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, please be more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.94,0:13:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop sucking the water up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.71,0:14:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. This discus is a tank for saving sucked water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hole... It has an automatic recapture system, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.62,0:14:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much I break, it repairs again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.87,0:14:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The cross-marked discus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. It's this one. This one's controlling all the discuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the control room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.18,0:15:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it! This is the main computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, this is the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this crystal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The main computer is getting protect by the crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If I step inside, I would get torn to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.22,0:15:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I should turn in the same direction the tornado goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like the temperature is going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This machine was the temperature regulator of the discus.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This was ordering other discuses to suck water up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it! Water in the discus froze and increased in volume and the discus burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! The cross-marked discus...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Horett doesn't have to be chased.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-Doctor Ochanomizu. -Ah, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, I took care of Alsore's discus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.19,0:17:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right now. Please stop the hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, how nice. So... What about the girl called Horett?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's waiting for me in a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.78,0:18:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.37,0:18:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I took care of the discus. Robots aren't coming anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.10,0:18:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett, but since there are no discus, you must not be able to go back to your planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to come to my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'd like to go back. Everyone's waiting for water.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:19:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This planet is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a lot of water and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett, in fact... To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.70,0:19:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Your, your planet Alsore is now gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It exploded two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Horett.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett, you can now live in the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-You can come to my house... -Thank you, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I will show you how I really look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, I was disguising as a human
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to not surprise people,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't need this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom, please bury me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Her body's melting.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Something came out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Alsoreans were plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.41,0:20:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,After One Year
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it? It's better than last year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran! Don't ride it like a bulldozer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.73,0:21:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad. Where did Atom go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.11,0:21:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he around?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one who wanted to come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He went somewhere by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Atom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's Uran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Horett, I'm leaving. I'll come back next year again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Uran!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.67,0:22:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant robot Pluto, with million horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The villain Sultan is trying to destroy all famous robots of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.79,0:22:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Pluto, it doesn't mean anything to become the strongest robot in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Give Uran back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming for you, Pluto. Screw million horsepower!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to lose to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy, "The Biggest Robot on Earth (Part One)." Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.78,0:22:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Astro Boy "The Biggest Robot on Earth (Part One)"
